{{Otheruses|The Aviary}}
'''The Aviary''' was the neighborhood of [[Vlarnya]] on [[Courkrus]] where the [[Invids|Invid]] [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] crews all lived. Few civilians resided there. Several cantinas, such as the Crash, and the Mynock Hole, are based here.<ref name="I,Jedi">[[I, Jedi]]</ref>

